content:
Just discovered that several RustSec bugs were assigned CVE numbers on Jan 22 and Feb 09. I'll create a PR on advisory-db to update them this weekend or early next week. If another person can work on it before then, that's also appreciated :)
https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvekey.cgi?keyword=rust

Going over the list right now. It seems that https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2021-21235 and https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2021-21269 are only listed on CVE without corresponding RUSTSEC entries.
